Hao Li (hl824) , Mingwei Tian (mt643)

CS4411 Project 5 - Ad-Hoc Networking

The project is finished in Windows to be available for testing.
It is merged back into this Linux version at the end.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
The progamming is done in the Windows/VS2010 64bit environment.

instant_msg.c implements a simple messenger.

Due to limited availability of machines, this project has not been tested on
networks with more than 3 nodes.

